### Referrer Management API - REST Client
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@referrerId = 698c432ab24c050d9011686f

### 1. GET All Referrers
GET {{baseUrl}}/referrers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. GET Single Referrer
GET {{baseUrl}}/referrer/{{referrerId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. CREATE New Referrer
POST {{baseUrl}}/referrer/add
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Dr. Ahmed Khan",
  "contactNumber": "01712345678",
  "degree": "MBBS, FCPS (Medicine)",
  "details": "Senior Consultant at United Hospital",
  "type": "doctor",
  "commissionType": "percentage",
  "commissionValue": 15,
  "isActive": true
}

### 4. UPDATE Referrer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/referrer/edit/{{referrerId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Dr. Ahmed Khan",
  "contactNumber": "01712345678",
  "degree": "MBBS, FCPS (Medicine), MD",
  "details": "Senior Consultant at United Hospital - Updated",
  "type": "doctor",
  "commissionType": "percentage",
  "commissionValue": 18,
  "isActive": true
}

### 5. DEACTIVATE Referrer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/referrer/{{referrerId}}/deactivate

### 6. ACTIVATE Referrer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/referrer/{{referrerId}}/activate

### 7. DELETE Referrer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/referrer/{{referrerId}}